BBUUGGSS
       Searching for package names and versions can lead to both  false  posi-
       tives  and  false  negatives.  The CPE matching documentation specifies
       greater than and less than logic.  ffaallccoo  and  other  tools  use  regex
       matches  and the fact that the NVD data provides an intended comprehen-
       sive list of impacted versions for each _C_V_E number.

